nodes.text: 50 Greatest Reasons to Love the Star Wars Prequels!

50 Greatest Reasons to Love the Star Wars Prequels! is an article published in Star Wars Insider 147. Several Star Wars actors, crew members, writers, and fans were asked to reveal what they loved most about the prequel trilogy. It was later reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2015.
